Name: Terra Incognito - Antarctica 1911
About the game: The race to the South Pole is back on.... Terra incognita or terra ignota (Latin 'unknown land') is a term used in cartography for regions that have not been mapped or documented. ​Go back in time and participate in the glory and the drama of the race to the South Pole. Prepare your crew and set the strategy to reach the South Pole in this fast paced real time strategy game. * Discover a viable route to the South Pole * Ensure your explorers remain in supply and warm enough to survive * Progress to the South Pole at maximum speed to reach the top of the leaderboard * Deploy supply camps, dogs and ladders to reach the objective * Interact and adapt to the environment to gain an advantage * Keep a constant watch on the weather conditions * Gain experience points and upgrade the explorer's skillset * Avoid contact with the predatory and dangerous Ice Bear ​Battle the elements, survive the hardships and above all else, plan properly...
